### Test Kiosk API Endpoints
### Make sure the backend is running on localhost:5055

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:5055/api/health

### Get Calendar Events
GET http://localhost:5055/api/calendar

### Get Tasks
GET http://localhost:5055/api/tasks

### Get Metadata
GET http://localhost:5055/api/meta

### Force Refresh (requires admin token)
POST http://localhost:5055/api/admin/refresh
Authorization: Bearer change_me

### Test with invalid admin token (should fail)
POST http://localhost:5055/api/admin/refresh
Authorization: Bearer invalid_token
